{"id":15548,"date":"2024-03-12T13:58:49","date_gmt":"2024-03-12T13:58:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?p=15548"},"modified":"2024-03-12T17:06:02","modified_gmt":"2024-03-12T17:06:02","slug":"aganor-seeg-formation-aux-exigences-de-la-norme-iso-14001-systeme-de-management-environnemental","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/2024\/03\/12\/aganor-seeg-formation-aux-exigences-de-la-norme-iso-14001-systeme-de-management-environnemental\/","title":{"rendered":"AGANOR-SEEG : Formation aux exigences de la norme ISO 14001 : \u00ab Syst\u00e8me de Management Environnemental \u00bb"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-796372d95aa1a64660310f9699c8cb62\" ><p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Dans le cadre des activit\u00e9s de la Direction de la Promotion de la Qualit\u00e9, l\u2019Agence Gabonaise de Normalisation (AGANOR) a organis\u00e9 du 12 au 14 d\u00e9cembre 2023, une session de formation au b\u00e9n\u00e9fice d\u2019une cuv\u00e9e d\u2019agents de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 d\u2019Energie et d\u2019Eau du Gabon (SEEG).<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Ax\u00e9e sur le r\u00e9f\u00e9rentiel ISO 14001, cette formation a permis aux agents de la SEEG de comprendre les exigences de la norme, en plus de leur donner les \u00e9l\u00e9ments n\u00e9cessaires \u00e0 la structuration d\u2019un syst\u00e8me de management environnemental.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Ainsi, ces agents pourront enclencher au sein de leur \u00e9tablissement, le processus de r\u00e9novation de la d\u00e9marche environnementale selon ISO 14001 : 2015.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Pour rappel, l\u2019AGANOR accompagne les entit\u00e9s souhaitant s\u2019inscrire dans :<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">\u2022 Une d\u00e9marche de certification ;<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">\u2022 L\u2019am\u00e9lioration de l\u2019image de l\u2019entreprise ;<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">\u2022 La conservation des ressources et la r\u00e9duction des d\u00e9chets ;<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">\u2022 Une d\u00e9marche de conformit\u00e9 aux exigences l\u00e9gales.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Notre expertise vous dotera d&rsquo;une ma\u00eetrise des meilleures pratiques en mati\u00e8re de Syst\u00e8mes de Management Environnemental et vous permettra de r\u00e9duire les impacts environnementaux n\u00e9gatifs li\u00e9s \u00e0 vos activit\u00e9s.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-15551 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14001SEEG-e1710262683660.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"324\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-15550 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/14001-e1710262496574.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"324\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; Dans le cadre des activit\u00e9s de la Direction de la Promotion de la Qualit\u00e9, l\u2019Agence Gabonaise de Normalisation (AGANOR) a organis\u00e9 du 12 au 14 d\u00e9cembre 2023, une session de formation au b\u00e9n\u00e9fice d\u2019une cuv\u00e9e d\u2019agents de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 d\u2019Energie et d\u2019Eau du Gabon (SEEG). Ax\u00e9e sur le r\u00e9f\u00e9rentiel ISO 14001, cette formation a&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15552,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[60],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15548"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15548"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15548\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":15573,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15548\/revisions\/15573"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15552"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15548"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15548"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15548"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}